Package provided.discovery.impl.model

package provided.discovery.impl.model
Optional convenience classes and interfaces for use in the "model" side of a system.
Author:
Stephen Wong (c) 2018
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    IDiscoveryModelToViewAdapter<TRemoteStub>
    Adapter used by some ADiscoveryModel implementations to connect to their "view".
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    ADiscoveryModel<TRemoteStub extends Remote>
    Abstract Discovery Model that provides common services to its implementations
    DiscoveryConnector
    Optional utility class to create a connection to the discovery server.
    DiscoveryModel<TRemoteStub extends Remote>
    Full featured ADiscoverModel that supports BOTH publishing an endpoint to a discovery server and connecting to endpoints on the discovery server.
    DiscoveryModelPubOnly<TRemoteStub extends Remote>
    An ADiscoveryModel that only supports publishing an endpoint to the discovery server but NOT connecting to end points.
    DiscoveryModelWatchOnly<TRemoteStub extends Remote>
    An ADiscoveryModel that only supports watching the discovery server and connecting to end points.
    RemoteAPIStubFactory<TRemoteStub extends Remote>
    Optional convenience factory for a specific API that can take an IEndPointData object and return the Registry-bound API-specific stub associated with the endpoint.
